that really brought this to fruition for me was that we realized that you had one company A was providing this service, and then company B was providing the same service. What we heard and what we all received in our packet is a request now of, I believe, $188,000 requesting funding back to the Armstrong Ambulance Company because the city has not fulfilled their requirement for the money that

