But I think this council realizes when I ask for an audit, and maybe my council didn't believe that was needed, but this is the exact reason why I want an audit. Not for the fact that we're saying that someone's stealing something or something illegal is going on. But when you're seeing the mismanagement of funds to the levels that we're seeing, with the loss of revenue that we were

