we were getting from Armstrong Ambulance, for instance, the questions that we have with our contracted services, and how many contracts we're hearing that aren't in compliance today. When we see the monies that are leaving the city because of lawsuits and settlements, when you see us fighting 40B projects, which you can't beat, you can't win,

