362
02:40:40,162 --> 02:41:07,735
So, there's a lot of questions that have to deal with maybe this administration doesn't like to hear what's best for this community, but wants to hear what's best for them. So, thank you. Thank you, Councilor Scarpelli. On the motion of Councilor Scarpelli, seconded by. On the motion approved by Councilor Scarpelli as amended, seconded by Councilor Mullane.

