03:12:16,709 --> 03:12:38,967
a body gets, that the council appoints, or the council confirms appointments to these boards, that means that they appear before the council in public, and we vote on it as a public body. It shouldn't be done by email. Thank you, Councilor Lemming. Councilor Scarpelli.

