03:14:41,142 --> 03:15:07,754
Like, the people who get to make decisions in Medford shouldn't be the same people who always get to make decisions in Medford. We need to be able to present everybody publicly. We need to have new and different people having opportunities, and we need everybody to see publicly all of this information. Neutrally, every time Henry gets appointed to a new position, we need to see his resume. I'm sorry, Henry.

