03:15:07,754 --> 03:15:26,468
His only advantage should be his incredible ability to charm a public body. Exactly. And his beautiful smile. Yes. No. And I think that's fair. I mean, I think there's three options. I think we can approve these and say we're not approving them again unless you follow a formal process. Then we can table them for two weeks and say,

