please follow a formal process or we can approve some and not others. You know, I think there's two things there. To be honest, like there was significant pushback. I really don't want to slow down the boards and commissions. If we table it, I'm going to get a bunch of people being like, why did we table this? Send them to me. I'll table it and send them to me. Blame it on me. So, you know. I officially take the blame.

